  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Fisher's Idle! Immerse yourself in the relaxed world of fishing, where you can buy and manage fishing boats to build a thriving fishing empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923170/extras/f2502013177ce16e34a3e9ce9305253c.poster.avif?t=1754588507\" width=800 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923170/extras/f2502013177ce16e34a3e9ce9305253c.webm?t=1754588507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923170/extras/f2502013177ce16e34a3e9ce9305253c.mp4?t=1754588507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Fisher's Idle you can:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Buy fishing boats</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest your money in various fishing boats, each bringing in different amounts of money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Automatic income</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your boats always make money (unless they are broken), even when you are not actively playing. Enjoy progress even by doing nothing and let the game run in the background!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Micromanagement</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize your fishing network through clever management and strategic upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxed gameplay</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sit back and watch your income steadily grow as you occasionally make adjustments to maximize your business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923170/extras/9402d3c13bb2cded6a88c7454462d814.avif?t=1754588507\" width=588 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the perfect blend of active strategy and passive income and become the ultimate fishing tycoon!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Fisher's Idle! Immerse yourself in the relaxed world of fishing, where you can buy and manage fishing boats to build a thriving fishing empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923170/extras/f2502013177ce16e34a3e9ce9305253c.poster.avif?t=1754588507\" width=800 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923170/extras/f2502013177ce16e34a3e9ce9305253c.webm?t=1754588507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923170/extras/f2502013177ce16e34a3e9ce9305253c.mp4?t=1754588507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Fisher's Idle you can:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Buy fishing boats</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest your money in various fishing boats, each bringing in different amounts of money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Automatic income</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your boats always make money (unless they are broken), even when you are not actively playing. Enjoy progress even by doing nothing and let the game run in the background!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Micromanagement</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize your fishing network through clever management and strategic upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxed gameplay</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sit back and watch your income steadily grow as you occasionally make adjustments to maximize your business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923170/extras/9402d3c13bb2cded6a88c7454462d814.avif?t=1754588507\" width=588 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the perfect blend of active strategy and passive income and become the ultimate fishing tycoon!</p>",
